for you tonight.

00:05.702 --> 00:06.717
Harley Carter,

00:06.742 --> 00:09.271
star of TV's number one
detective drama Call Carter,

00:09.363 --> 00:11.868
and his wife, actress and
supermodel Winter Wood,

00:11.893 --> 00:14.088
