01:08.496 --> 01:10.130
Yeah, I'm not going to
be able to make that.

01:10.154 --> 01:12.043
See, I'm at the beach in Canada.

01:13.557 --> 01:15.237
Okay, you know what,
let me talk to Rhonda.

01:18.041 --> 01:20.475
Yeah, well, tell her I don't
want to talk to her either.

01:20.510 --> 01:21.549
Thanks.

